-medium\">Chinedu Eze</span></div><span>Jan 3, 2026</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-emerald-600 font-medium text-xs group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\">Read More<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></div></div></a><a class=\"block group\" href=\"/blog/8\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm overflow-hidden h-full group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-200 to-teal-200 relative flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-white/25 text-5xl\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-12 w-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden border-transparent [a&amp;]:hover:bg-secondary/90 absolute top-3 left-3 text-xs font-medium bg-teal-100 text-teal-700\">Community Stories</span></div><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm leading-snug line-clamp-2 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">How Our Community in Lagos is Redefining Local Commerce</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-3 mb-3\">Lagos&#x27;s PostAll community has grown by 200% in the past year. Discover how sellers, freelancers, and buyers are creating a thriving local marketplace ecosystem together.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"h-5 w-5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-emerald-700\">ET</span></div><span class=\"font-medium\">Editorial Team</span></div><span>Dec 30, 2024</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-emerald-600 font-medium text-xs group-hover:gap-2 transition-all\">Read More<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></div></div></a><a class=\"block group\" href=\"/blog/9\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm overflow-hidden h-full group-hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-200\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200 to-orange-200 relative flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-white/25 text-5xl\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-12 w-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 